title: Malaysia Consumer Spending
description: Consumer Spending in Malaysia increased to 235858 MYR Million in the third quarter of 2022 from 219516 MYR Million in the second quarter of 2022. Consumer Spending in Malaysia averaged 138235.07 MYR Million from 2005 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 422452 MYR Million in the first quarter of 2022 and a record low of 56768 MYR Million in the second quarter of 2005. This page provides - Malaysia Consumer Spending - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of Statistics, Malaysia
